<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يُقَالُ <span class="c2">(١)</span>: القَيْسِيُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالُ:</span> البَهْرَانِيُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالُ:</span> اليَشْكُرِيُّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ حَرْبِ بْنِ شَدَّادٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
